      "rationale": "The pedicle screw and rod were modeled as continuum solid bodies with Ti-6Al-4V bilinear isotropic hardening. Augmented Lagrange contact was used at the screw-rod interface. Model form is consistent with the physics of quasi-static metal plasticity and is well-established for this class of implant simulation."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
