      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from certified coupon tests on production-lot Ti-6Al-4V; geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of test specimens.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus were derived from uniaxial tensile coupon tests on the same production lot as the test constructs. Screw and rod cross-sectional dimensions were measured by CMM to ±0.01 mm. Input uncertainty was propagated via Monte Carlo sampling (N=500)."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
