    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence COU. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is mitigated by the breadth of quantitative output comparison evidence and the sponsor's commitment to supplemental post-market testing. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory acceptance of the FEA modeling framework for this COU.",
